{"tid":2002262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】德研究推算　實際感染人數為官方數 10 倍　逾兩成人無病徵","createTime":"2020-05-05T05:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T05:47:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a641965a8f4a12380dce18c84f72f0c6e5e0544","tid":2002262,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"波恩大學團隊周一 (4/5) 公佈的實地檢測指，德國感染武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 的人數可能是官方確診病例的 10 倍，當中約五分之一的感染者毫無症狀，提醒民眾仍要注意冠狀病毒 SARS-CoV-2 可由無病徵者傳播的危機。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，德國進一步宣佈放寬社交隔離措施，博物館、理髮店、教堂和更多汽車工廠在嚴格條件下將重新開放........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\nThe Guardian, German Covid-19 cases 'may be 10 times higher than official figures&rsquo;, 4 May 2020<br />\nReuters, German study suggests infections are 10 times the number of confirmed cases, 4 May 2020<br />\n<br />\n文／Alan Chiu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BE%B7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8E%A8%E7%AE%97-%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E7%82%BA%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%95%B8-10-%E5%80%8D-%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E7%97%85%E5%BE%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25AE%2597-%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2595%25B8-10-%25E5%2580%258D-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BE%25B5%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=7071a9b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25AE%2597-%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259A%259B%